column1: gobel is a noun meaning "walled (fortified) settlement" in Sindarin.
The word contains the element pêl "encircle".
See also the collective prefix go-.
* Amon Obel = "Hill of the Walled Settlement"
* http://www.jrrvf.com/hisweloke/sindar/online/sindar/dict-sd-en.html Hiswelókës Sindarin Dictionary compiled by Didier Willis
